results.title: Ombre baby quilt
results.description:

This beautiful and timeless modern ombre letters fabric from Art Gallery fabric's Capsule Collection is so versatile. 

This could be a baby tummy time mat - perfect for when you need or want to put your precious bundle down on the floor, grass or beach safely and comfortably. 

It is equally at home being used as a crib quilt and later as wall decor for the nursery...or I can make you two so it can be both at same time!

Perfect for your Valentine,to show your love for someone, for a baby shower or your Mum!

results.description:

All 139handcrafted items are constructed and hand painted/hand lettered by me, Katie Bartel. I enjoy creating one-of-a-kind pieces using naturally aged pine wood from our local mill, or authentic, 100+ year old reclaimed wood that we have recovered from local barns that have been torn down. What makes these pieces unique is the natural beauty and texture of the aged wood contrasting with crisp lettering and imagery that is hand painted on them. results.title: Be Wild,  Copper Bracelet, Adventure, Wildflower, Hippie, Wild and Free, Tshirt Wrap Bracelet, Boho Jewelry, Cotton Wrap Bracelet (008)
results.description:
Go on adventure. Do the things. Love what and who you love. Be Wild!

BW Design Studio offers quality copper wrap bracelets that make perfect gifts or a great addition to your jewelry collection.

Quick Description:
*24g Copper plates measure 1.75" x .79"
*Wraps are recycled (by manufacturer) woven cotton wraps

Copper Plates:
I use high quality 24 gauge copper plates that are then etched with your design. Over time, copper will oxidize and give the plate a patina look. This can easily be removed with steel wool or polish if you desire.

Wraps:
With your order, you will receive 1 yard of recycled cotton tie. This is generally enough string to wrap around your wrist three times and tie. I love tying a bow, but you can also tie in a knot. Just know, the wrap may stretch and the knot will need to be retied.

Charms:
Charms are not included with the bracelets. They can be purchased separately in my shop. There are several sections to browse and if you don't see what you're looking for, custom orders are always welcome!

Cant find a charm or plate that fits your needs? Custom orders are always welcome! Each plate is limited to 4-6 words depending on length. Any charm design can also be a plate design!

My wrap bracelets make excellent gifts. Select gift wrap at checkout to have your wrap come with a mini version of the packaging card, small organza bag and box.

Your wrap is safe to wear while exercising and showering. Please note this will add to the patina quicker as well as wear on the wrap (including stretching). To properly care for your wrap, I recommend storing them in a dry area and not wearing in water. Copper is super easy to polish back to a shine if you wish.

Shipping:
My current turn around time is 7-10 business days. Due to the etching process, this can't be rushed.

USPS provides the following shipping estimates. Please note that these are estimates and USPS occasionally experiences delays, especially during high volume periods.
First Class- 2-5 Business Days
Priority Shipping 2-3 Business Days
Express Shipping 1-2 Business Days
First Class International--Varies
Priority International 14 Business Days
